  bottle of wine) for only $95! Every Friday night hilarious comedians from
  The Bay Area and beyond perform at Barrel Proof Lounge. Stick around afte
 r for late-night karaoke! Fresh lineup of funny each Friday.\n\nThis Week:
  Jon Lehre (host) Ajay Damodaran Chris Ferdinandson Headliner: Jalisa Robi
 nson\n\nJalisa Robinson brings her sometimes-deadpan\, sometimes-sparkling
  style to everything from race to the patriarchy to getting hit on at Whol
 e Foods. A native midwesterner\, she now lives in Los Angeles.\n\nShe’s 
 opened for Hannibal Burress and she regularly performs at Punchline San Fr
 ancisco\, the Set-Up LA\, Don't Tell Comedy\, Rooster T. Feathers\, San Jo
 se Improv\, Alameda Comedy Club\, and Cheaper Than Therapy where she’s a
 lso an alumnus artist resident and producer.\n\nShe's performed at comedy 
 festivals including SF Sketchfest and Oakland Comedy Festival and she was 
 a San Francisco International Comedy Competition Semi-Finalist (2022).\n\n
 21+ Doors - 7p / Show - 8p $15adv / $20door\n\nCheck out **www.BarrelProo
 fLounge.com** for all sorts of good times ahead.
