DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260314T123000
UID:2603092gYLLqT5G0C9aOwnq8b5xQ
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a 2-hour class designed to inspire and equip garde
 ners of all levels to grow delicious\, healthy tomatoes. Legendary local h
 eirloom tomato grower and Gold Ridge Organic Farms' neighbor\, Larry Wagne
 r\, will cover the essential techniques to help you succeed — from choos
 ing the right varieties to harvesting ripe\, flavorful fruit.\n\nLarry and
  his wife Cris have spent 25 years growing 400 heirloom tomato plants and 
 over 70 varietals on the nearby Volkerts Family Ranch. They supply restaur
 ants\, donate to nonprofits\, and share their harvest with friends and nei
 ghbors.\n\nLarry will walk you through every key step: seed starting\, soi
 l prep\, planting\, watering\, pruning\, seed saving\, and more. You'll le
 ave with practical tips\, fresh inspiration\, and your very own heirloom t
 omato plant!\n\nMorning tea will be served.
LOCATION:Gold Ridge Organic Farms
URL:https://www.exploretock.com/gold-ridge-organic-farms/event/594045/grow
 ing-great-tomatoes-with-larry-the-tomato-guy
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
