 s Or Shots Included With Ticket Purchase\n\n🚫 No Cover At All Bars\, Mi
 d Party\, & After Party\n\n🥤 Crawl With US Stadium Party Cup and Bottle
  Opener Lanyard\n\n💚💛 Green & Gold Beads\n\n🍻 Exclusive Drink Spe
