BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Ralph Barbosa: The Red 40 Tour
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T190000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T190000
UID:260305U3cBjneNiEWu2EetydjCpQ
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nLive Nation Presents \n\nRalph Barbosa: T
 he Red 40 Tour\n\nSunday\, March 15\, 2026\n\n7:00 pm\n\nBUY TICKETS\n\nAG
 E RESTRICTION: 18 and above \n\n \n\nOne of the shyest attention hogs ever
  to do comedy\, Ralph Barbosa’s disarming and laid-back style has made h
 im a stand-out on stage\, on TV\, and as host of the Formula Bean YouTube 
 channel with Luis Cisneros. Last summer\, Barbosa premiered his second hou
 r-long stand-up special\, Ralph Barbosa: Planet Bosa\, as part of Hulu’s
  new Hularious comedy brand. \n\nHis first hour-long stand-up special\, Ra
 lph Barbosa: Cowabunga\, premiered on Netflix on October 31\, 2023\, and r
 anked as the \\#3 TV show on Netflix throughout its first week on the serv
 ice. \n\nIn July 2024\, Barbosa was selected as one of Variety’s 10 Comi
 cs to Watch for 2024 and toured theaters throughout North America\, includ
 ing two sold-out theater shows as part of the Netflix Is A Joke Fest 2024\
 , as well as hosting the kick-off show. 2023 was Barbosa’s break-out yea
 r\, during which he was a guest on The Joe Rogan Experience\, made his deb
 ut on The Tonight Show Starring Jimmy Fallon\, and performed Comedy Centra
 l Stand-up Featuring: Ralph Barbosa\, which topped 6 million views on YouT
 ube. \n\nBarbosa also starred in the HBO Max comedy special\, Entre Nos: T
 he Winners 3 in 2022\, and earlier that year his Don’t Tell Comedy perfo
 rmance was released on YouTube and now has over 6 million views. \n\nPlati
 num Tickets are tickets that are dynamically priced up and down based on d
 emand. Platinum Tickets are not part of VIP packages – they are tickets 
 only. \n\nPlatinum Seating provides fans with direct access to securing so
 me of the best seats in the venue at market value. The market value for Pl
 atinum Seating is subject to change based on the overall demand and popula
 rity for the event.  Platinum Seating allows fans to purchase tickets in 
 a safe and secure environment without running the risk of purchasing ticke
 ts that may be considered lost\, stolen\, or counterfeit. \n\nTHIRD PARTY 
 RESELLERS\n\nDon’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who use bots 
 to buy tickets and then mark up their prices. The only safe way to protect
  your purchase and guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is to work 
 directly with us: through our website\, by phone\, or at our box office in
  Santa Rosa. Plus\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are easily
  accessible by phone or at the box office to provide customer support.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/ralph-barbosa26/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bottle Baby Breakfast Club
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T160000
UID:260312OHjYjtfYeU-JyJ37mTZpgg
DESCRIPTION:Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission\n\nAt Goa
 tlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a second chan
 ce to animals who need it most.\n\nWe were recently called to rescue three
  baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and they need 
 bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.\n\nThat’s
  Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club\n\nStarting March 6th\,
  join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-feeding and cuddling
  our newest rescues while supporting their care.\n\nYour $250 donation \\(
 covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings\\) includes admission for u
 p to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to Goatlandia.\n\nCom
 e share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give these little ones the
  future they deserve.
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Breathless Sparkling Wines "Women's History Celebration Sundays"
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T120000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T140000
UID:260312-XpD_jveL0-H-rVu7QUBTQ
DESCRIPTION:Breathless Sparkling Wines is hosting a speaker and luncheon 
 series which will be held every Sunday in March at the winery’s tranquil
  outdoor garden in Healdsburg to honor Women’s History Month. \n\nThe 
 “Breathless Women’s History Celebration Sundays” series aligns with
  the National Women’s History Alliance’s 2026 theme\, “Leading the 
 Change: Women Shaping a Sustainable Future\,” which recognizes women adv
 ancing environmental\, economic and social sustainability through leadersh
 ip\, innovation and community impact.\n\nEach Breathless Wines Sparkling G
 arden Luncheon will be paired with a featured female speaker whose work re
 flects the evolving role of women in shaping industries and communities\, 
 sparkling wines\, and wines paired with a lunch prepared by Chef Beryl Adl
 er of Healdsburg's Acorn Café. Visit BreathlessWines.com for more.
LOCATION:Breathless Wines
URL:https://breathlesswines.com/events/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Joseph Jewell Wines Open House
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T120000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T170000
UID:260311Vrpkt0wIq0SpzZcgWzLnlA
DESCRIPTION:Joseph Jewell Open House\n\nVisit our charming town of Forestv
 ille Sunday\, March 15th\, 2026 for our Open House. This event is a perfec
 t opportunity to mingle with fellow wine lovers\, share stories\, and take
  home your favorite selections of our Joseph Jewell lineup of wines. Enjoy
  seasonal bites with our new release wines and meet our winemaker and foun
 der.\n\n$20 per person tasting fee charged during visit. Complimentary for
  Joseph Jewell and Jewell Club Members. Tasting fees for non-members will 
 be waived with a one-bottle or more purchase per person.\n\nMake a reserva
 tion through the link. If you don't see the time you'd like to book\, plea
