UID:260304N35zjOWFUkaYilIWZDA8Ww
DESCRIPTION:Join us Sunday\, March 15th at the Hill Community Room to lear
 n about democratic socialism. We will discuss the ways in which our local 
 Marin chapter of the Democratic Socialists of America \\(DSA\\) is buildin
 g working-class power right here in Marin County. Some of our current effo
 rts include helping to lead the fight to get ICE out of Marin\, Palestine 
 solidarity work\, and organizing in solidarity with tenants and labor unio
 ns. Come and meet local Marin DSA members and learn how you can help build
  a progressive movement right here in your backyard. You can RSVP here: h
 ttps://marin-dsa.org/101
