DESCRIPTION:Join Spreckels Theatre Education Program this winter for our 8
  week teen production class of Between the Lines Jr\, for ages 13-17.\n\n
  An outsider in a new town and a new school\, Delilah seeks comfort in th
 e pages of her favorite book\, where she feels heard and understood by the
  handsome Prince Oliver. But as the lines between fantasy and reality begi
 n to blur in extraordinary ways\, Delilah realizes her dreams in the real
  world are worth fighting for.
LOCATION:Spreckels Center for the Performing Arts
