UID:260305PR_tWI5f00ulKLnl1_jIGw
DESCRIPTION:Tuesday\, March 17th\n\nDance\, celebrate\, and don’t get pi
 nched!\n\nThis St. Patrick’s Day\, grab your best \\(green\\) dancin' sh
 oes and come on down to WonderStump! Pardon the Interruption serves up sk
 a-fueled funk\, rock\, reggae\, soul\, and upbeat jams-- turning the night
  into a full-body celebration. High spirits\, happy feet\, and serious bou
