UID:260224vmY9z-Y1XUu-R5QCEeZWMA
DESCRIPTION:NFL said no.\n\nSt. Patrick said yes. 🍀\n\nApparently we we
 re “overqualified” to stand quietly as halftime trees… so we’re ta
 king our talents where they belong — straight to the party.\n\nJoin Wond
 er Bread 5 for a dangerously fun St. Patrick’s Day throwdown at Coyote S
 onoma. This is the rare holiday where showing up festive is encouraged and
  questionable decisions feel culturally appropriate.\n\nMarch 17 | 6–8 P
 M\n\nPerfect excuse to start early\, be home at a reasonable hour… or ab
 solutely not.\n\nWear green. Bring friends. Hydrate irresponsibly \\(with 
