SUMMARY:Bottle Baby Breakfast Club
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T160000
UID:260312K_5D3-DB2kKmYjJkziTv_g
DESCRIPTION:Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission\n\nAt Goa
 tlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a second chan
 ce to animals who need it most.\n\nWe were recently called to rescue three
  baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and they need 
 bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.\n\nThat’s
  Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club\n\nStarting March 6th\,
  join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-feeding and cuddling
  our newest rescues while supporting their care.\n\nYour $250 donation \\(
 covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings\\) includes admission for u
 p to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to Goatlandia.\n\nCom
 e share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give these little ones the
  future they deserve.
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Quench at Copia: "GOAT"-ed Grapes- Chardonnay Edition
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T183000
UID:260311igxCCiHwdkizbp1MhslcbA
DESCRIPTION:CIA at Copia is proud to be the home of the newest wine tastin
 g experience and podcast series\, Quench at Copia\, with Master Sommeli
 er Andrea Immer Robinson. You will get to be part of a live studio audien
 ce through a guided tasting with special guests from the culinary and win
 e industries who will join along the way. Each event invites you to le
 arn and connect through exceptional wines\, thoughtful pairings\, and liv
 ely conversation.  \n\nWhy does Chardonnay taste so different from place
  to place—and why does limestone matter so much? Find out at a live\, in
 -person tasting during CIA at Copia’s Quench at Copia series led by 
 Master Sommelier Andrea Immer Robinson with special guest and legendary w
 inemaker\, David Ramey. In this experience\, you’ll be focusing on o
 ne of the “GOAT”-ed Grapes: Chardonnay! You’ll explore standout
  Chardonnay styles side by side\, paired with bites designed to amplify fl
 avor and texture. Expect “aha” moments\, lively conversation\, and g
 reat white wine.\n\nThis experience will also be paired with a “Taste o
 f The Grove” – a sample of a dish from The Grove Restaurant curat
 ed by our former CIA student and Michelin-starred chef.
LOCATION:CIA at Copia (The Culinary Institute of America at Copia)
URL:https://www.ciaatcopia.com/quench-wine-podcast-at-copia/?utm_source=we
 bsite&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=quench-at-copia-city-spark
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Quantum Coherence with Anistara Ma Ka
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T183000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260318T203000
UID:260309UWWDov0pHUG3dv5NEXCqEw
DESCRIPTION:Cultivating Wholeness Through Energy Alignment\n\nDuring these
  gatherings\, Anistara will be sharing a meditation by Dr. Joe Dispenza\, 
 whose teachings she has practiced for years. Having attended two of his li
 ve retreats\, she witnessed profound transformations and healing stories t
 hat deepened her devotion to coherence work and the intelligence of the qu
 antum field.\n\nEach session invites you into a state of heart–mind cohe
 rence — where the nervous system settles\, the body relaxes\, and the en
 ergy field begins to harmonize. Within the amplified energetic environment
  of the EES\, participants are guided to align with wholeness\, clarity\, 
 and expanded possibility.\n\nThis is not a lecture or workshop — it is a
  space to practice. To breathe. To regulate.\n\nTo remember the innate int
 elligence within your body and energy system.\n\nWhether you are new to me
 ditation or experienced in quantum practices\, this monthly gathering offe
 rs a consistent container to reset\, recalibrate\, and return to coherence
 .\n\nCome as you are. Leave feeling aligned\, centered\, and more whole.\n
 \nAbout Anistara\n\nAnistara Ma Ka is a multidimensional guide\, best-sell
 ing author\, and transformational speaker devoted to supporting awakening 
 souls in remembering who they truly are. As the Founder of Ascension Unive
 rsity and the Mother of 11.11 Unified\, she guides individuals into embodi
 ed leadership\, sovereignty\, and alignment with New Earth consciousness t
 hrough her teachings\, transmissions\, and ceremonial work. An ordained Sa
 cred Portal Oracle of the Portal Priestess Mystery School and steward of J
 oy Oasis\, Anistara creates immersive retreats\, initiations\, and ceremon
 ies rooted in ancient wisdom and modern embodiment. Her work weaves energe
 tic leadership\, sacred remembrance\, and lived devotion—holding spaces 
 where transformation unfolds naturally and participants reconnect with the
 ir purpose\, presence\, and inner authority.
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/anistara/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
