DESCRIPTION:American Heart Association ACLS Certification Class \\(Blended
  Learning\\)\n\nAdvanced Cardiovascular Life Support\n\nThe AHA ACLS Certi
 fication Blended Learning class includes an online course followed by an i
 n-person Skills Session. This class is appropriate for initial ACLS certif
