BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cheese & Butter Classes
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T000000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T170000
UID:2603040lR17OxJkUCBddf7_FanpQ
DESCRIPTION:Join award-winning cheesemaker Sheana Davis and wine expert Be
 n Sessions for unforgettable cheese and butter making classes. Perfect fo
 r team building\, celebrations\, and educational events\, our classes are 
 interactive\, fun\, and easy for everyone. \n\nFrom classes on how to make
  Creme de Ricotta wheel to Mozzarella Pulling to butter-making classes\, g
 uests will always leave with a creamy treat to take home \\(if it makes it
  that far!\\) – so bring a small cooler with you.  \n\nFood has a remar
 kable ability to bring people together. \n\nCheesemaking classes are perfe
 ct for team-building activities\, company meetings\, team celebrations\, s
 taff events\, corporate fun\, bridal parties\, couples classes\, girlfrien
 d getaway weekends\, LGBT events\, EBT education courses\, and more. Class
 es held year-round on Thursday\, Friday\, and Saturday\, 12:00-2:00 and 3:
 30-5:30pm. \n\nSee the full schedule of all our cheese and butter making c
 lasses here.  \n\nWith each class\, we give back to the community by prov
 iding meals for food-insecure seniors in Sonoma Valley. After learning how
  to make cheese\, our guests can prepare these meals and write personal no
 tes for the seniors on the lids.  \n\nJoin us in making a positive impact
  while having fun and learning a new skill.   \n\nYour Cheesemaking Expe
 rience: \n\n\n\nBegin with local wine and an artisanal cheese tasting.\n\n
 Learn to make cheese and compound butter with everyday ingredients and too
 ls.\n\nEnjoy specialized classes for dishes like lasagna and gourmet grill
 ed cheeses.\n\nExclusive guest cheesemakers often share their techniques.\
 n\nIdeal for corporate events\, bridal parties\, getaways\, and more.\n\n\
 n\nSheana and Ben pride themselves on using ingredients readily available 
 in any local grocery store\, with cooking supplies used reside in most hom
 e cooks’ kitchens. Guest cheesemakers are often available to showcase th
 eir own cheeses and techniques\, making the class a truly unique experienc
 e. \n\nCheck the schedule for Wine Country-based cheesemaking classes.  
 \n\nCustomize Your Class:To arrange private or corporate classes at venues
  like Sonoma Fairmont Mission Inn or Silverado Resort\, contact us at she
 anadavis@gmail.com. We can help create a unique and unforgettable experien
 ce for your entire group! Private and corporate classes may be arranged an
 d are hosted at various Wine Country venues\, including The Fairmont Sonom
 a Mission Inn\, Silverado Resort\, The Lodge in Sonoma\, and private homes
  and estates. \n\nTo register: \n\nhttps://theepicureanconnection.com/even
 ts/
URL:https://www.farmtrails.org/event/cheese-butter-classes/2026-03-19/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
