DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260319T180000
UID:260312HWoVblekdEerverNj0qdRg
DESCRIPTION:Croix Estate Winery was founded by Jason Williams and acclaime
 d winemaker Kirk Venge\, whose roots in winemaking trace back generations 
 in Napa Valley. Williams began concepting the winery in 2009\, leading to 
 its first vintage in 2012 and the transformation of its Russian River Vall
 ey home. Venge\, who also owns Venge Vineyards and consults for top Napa p
 roducers\, brought a vision of minimal-intervention winemaking rooted in S
 onoma’s premier vineyard sites. Together\, they’ve built a brand defin
 ed by rustic luxury\, sustainability\, and a deep respect for the land. Co
 me enjoy Vinyl rarities and all time favorite Beatles songs\, including so
 lo works and later collaborations from the Fab Four and their friends. \n
 \nThis event is complimentary. Ages 21 and up only.
