UID:260107_rP6lW1bLkabHVrzG1thsg
DESCRIPTION:Whose ready to be a part of an amazing group of girls and yout
 h who are open minded and hearted—ready to make new friends AND develop 
 essential life skills to help them learn to live well?\n\nWe are now enrol
 ling for our School Year Wellness Workshops for girls in 3rd-8th grades.\n
