BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Womens Gathering: Art & Activism
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T190000
UID:260312dFlbjFhJjEK8xAcpmFp1kA
DESCRIPTION:**Women's Protest Art Gathering! Prepping for March 28th NO K
 INGS National Protest!**\n\nIf you've been feeling the need to do somethin
 g\, to express yourself\, please come! You can make posters\, signs\, pain
 t abstract\, release anger & energy\, do anything you feel needed. I'll ha
 ve lots of supplies\, examples of Protest Art.\n\n**⭐️BONUS: The Seba
 stopol Center for the Arts has put out a call for artists:** Resist and Pe
 rsist: Social (in)Justice\n\n*Use our Friday gathering to also Brainstorm 
 & Plan or Begin Your Art Entry for this show*\n\n"Artists have always resp
 onded at the forefront of cultural change. In times of unrest\, art does n
 ot stay silent. It speaks truth\, demands change\, mourns loss\, and envis
 ions hope. We are seeking powerful\, original works that reflect the momen
 t: art that confronts injustice\, reclaims identity\, honors resistance\, 
 or envisions hope." All mediums are welcome\, including poetry! We want t
 o hear your voice. Call Closes: May 1st\, 2026."
LOCATION:Full Circle Studio
URL:https://www.taradickinson.com/lets-create/workshops
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Bottle Baby Breakfast Club
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T160000
UID:26031246vwsKYGhE233aMSOhLYNw
DESCRIPTION:Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission\n\nAt Goa
 tlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a second chan
 ce to animals who need it most.\n\nWe were recently called to rescue three
  baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and they need 
 bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.\n\nThat’s
  Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club\n\nStarting March 6th\,
  join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-feeding and cuddling
  our newest rescues while supporting their care.\n\nYour $250 donation \\(
 covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings\\) includes admission for u
 p to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to Goatlandia.\n\nCom
 e share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give these little ones the
  future they deserve.
LOCATION:Goatlandia
URL:https://www.goatlandia.org/bottle-babies-breakfast-club
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
