DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T141500
UID:260214UzHKvo9pK0eagBHVdNcOlQ
DESCRIPTION:with devon hase\, MA\n\nStart or deepen your practice in this 
 accessible overview of meditation and mindfulness.\n\nExplore a range of a
 pproaches to gathering\, settling\, and focusing the heart and mind with o
 ne of Spirit Rock’s most beloved teachers. The Buddha taught many differ
 ent ways to meditate\, and we’ll help you find a practice that feels rig
 ht for you or strengthen an existing practice.
