SUMMARY:Volunteer Days: SSU Copeland Creek Corridor & Native Plant Garden
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T140000
UID:260213Gf23UQ8JTk6q_WybyWfhbA
DESCRIPTION:Join the effort to remove invasive plants\, plant new native p
 lants\, and generally clean up and beautify the Copeland Creek corridor an
 d Native Plant Garden.\n\nEmail myersn@sonoma.edu for more information and
  to sign up and receive location and logistical information.
