BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:MP Matador Promotions Presenta Carlos Daniels: Homenaje a Juan Gab
 riel - Mas Vivo Que Nunca 2026
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T200000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T200000
UID:260227t96GqvtHPkCfjDKaiNN1OQ
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nMP Matador Promotions Presenta\n\nCarlos 
 Daniels: Homenaje a Juan Gabriel – Mas Vivo Que Nunca 2026\n\nFriday\, M
 arch 20\, 2026\n\n8:00 pm\n\nBUY TICKETS \n\nAfter four successful tours a
 cross the US\, Colombian Latin-mariachi-pop singer\, songwriter\, and prod
 ucer Carlos Daniels is back with Más Vivo Que Nunca  – Juan Gabriel Tr
 ibute \\(More Alive Than Ever\\)\, a spectacle that thousands of fans acro
 ss the nation are waiting for. \n\nKnown as one of the best interpreters o
 f El Divo De Juarez’s music\, Daniels has conquered fans’ hearts with 
 impressive performances at renowned venues\, including five shows at the H
 ouse of Blues Mandalay Bay Casino in Las Vegas. On this new tour\, Daniels
 \, along with a Mariachi band\, is determined to touch your soul by revivi
 ng some of Gabriel’s greatest hits\, while delivering an unforgettable p
 erformance. Más Vivo Que Nunca – Juan Gabriel Tribute will bring you a 
 sea of emotions and memories\, promising they will keep you singing along 
 to every tune from the beginning until the end of the show. \n\n \n\nTHIRD
  PARTY RESELLERS\n\nDon’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who us
 e bots to buy tickets and then mark up their prices. The only safe way to 
 protect your purchase and guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is t
 o work directly with us: through our website\, by phone\, or at our box of
 fice in Santa Rosa. Plus\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are
  easily accessible by phone or at the box office to provide customer suppo
 rt.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/carlos-daniels26/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
