DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260320T103000
UID:251129AQS5cVi3kUGf_3rB7cq02w
DESCRIPTION:Step into the heart of Campovida's organic farming practices w
 ith our Taste and Tour - a genuine journey where the vineyard unfolds its 
 stories\, like two familiar friends catching up. Immerse yourself in the h
 istory of winemaking as our guides share tales of the vineyard's heritage\
 , tracing the evolution from humble beginnings to the exceptional wines we
  produce today. Feel the connection to the land as you touch the grapes an
 d absorb the essence of the very soil that defines our winemaking legacy. 
 Explore our 150 acres of thriving vineyards\, starting with the award-winn
 ing Viognier right in our front yard and moving on to the backyard for som
 e Sangiovese goodness. These vines\, like the stories they hold\, have bee
 n organically grown for decades. Farm = Life
