BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Cheese & Beer: Expert Pairings with Janet Fletcher Saturday @ CUVE
 R
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T110000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T120000
UID:26031157tgH-wWdkmSpnJPZ-Wq4Q
DESCRIPTION:Join James Beard Award-winning food journalist and Planet Chee
 se publisher Janet Fletcher for a tasting journey that illuminates the art
  of pairing cheese with beer\, in collaboration with CUVER Belgian Brewers
 . The author of Cheese & Beer\, Janet has taught cheese appreciation to th
 ousands of enthusiasts over the past 25 years. In this interactive seminar
 \, she will teach you the pairing basics and highlight the flavors\, textu
 res\, and aromas that make beer and cheese such a compelling match.\n\nEnj
 oy Janet’s pick of California artisan cheeses with a curated selection o
 f beers from CUVER Belgian Brewers\, a brewery inspired by traditional Bel
 gian brewing techniques and known for expressive\, food-friendly styles. T
 ogether\, Janet and the CUVER team will explore how classic Belgian-inspir
 ed beers can complement\, contrast with\, and elevate a wide variety of ch
 eeses.\n\nLearn practical pairing principles\, discover unexpected flavor 
 combinations\, and gain a deeper appreciation for both artisan cheese and 
 craft beer.\n\nWhether you’re a devoted cheese lover\, a knowledgeable c
 raft-beer fan\, or a novice simply eager to learn\, this seminar promises 
 insight\, inspiration\, and plenty of delicious discoveries.\n\nDate: Sat
 urday\, March 21\, 2026\n\nTime: 11:00am – 12:00pm\n\nLocation: CUVER 
 Belgian Brewers\; 7704 Bell Road\, Windsor\, CA 95492
LOCATION:CUVER Belgian Brewers
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/cheese-beer-expert-pair
 ings-with-janet-fletcher-saturday-cuver/18313383/2026-03-21T11
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Mary Blair: Mid-Century Magic Opening Celebration
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T160000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T190000
UID:26031117KC-bCfkEOVQDQGeued8g
DESCRIPTION:The Napa Valley Museum Yountville \\(NVMY\\) invites you to
  step into a world of imagination and color as we celebrate the opening of
  “Mary Blair: Mid-Century Magic” on March 21\, 2026 —a special exhi
 bition created by the Walt Disney Family Museum. Co-hosted by NVMY\, the 
 Walt Disney Family Museum\, and Tiki Oasis\, this opening celebration offe
 rs guests a first look into Mary Blair’s iconic playful palettes and whi
 msical spirit she brought to some of Disney’s most beloved movies.\n\nTh
 roughout the evening\, delightful surprises will unfold\, including a 60's
  inspired dance performance by The Devil-Ettes\, mid-century music by ou
 r resident DJ\, cocktails by Hanson of Sonoma Distillery\, and small bite
 s by Sushi Monkey. Guests are encouraged to attend in cocktail attire
  or mid-century 50s–60s style. \n\n4 p.m. First Look for Priority Acce
 ss\, Museum Member & MAC Pack includes signature cocktail created by Hans
 on of Sonoma Distillery and gift from the NVMY\n\n5-7 p.m. General Admiss
 ion: Celebration continues with cocktails\, sushi and music.\n\nJoin us as
  we toast to imagination and the radiant legacy of Mary Blair.
LOCATION:Napa Valley Museum
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/mary-blair-mid-century-
 magic-opening-celebration/18285242/2026-03-21T16
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
