DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260321T190000
UID:26022555VCjT-rg0eS7G-3k4xN3w
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a reception with the Artist\, March 21st fr
 om 5-7pm. The exhibition will be open from then until April 21st.\n\n"Hono
 ring this Land and its views helps me to remember who I am as a being who 
 walks in this beautiful environment. It is a reminder that the landscape i
 s as alive as I am alive\, and is something to be held in high regard and 
 cherished\, not for the richness of its resources but for itself alone." -
  Susan Hall
LOCATION:Erickson Fine Art Gallery
URL:https://www.ericksonfineartgallery.com/future-exhibitions
