 a Wiley's Wish Gift Basket worth over $500 and other items!**\n\nCome meet
  incredible\, **trained rescue dogs available for adoption**\, soak up the
  spring vibes\, and maybe even meet your future best friend. While you’r
 e here\, browse Pawsarotti’s beautifully curated selection of toys\, tre
 ats\, food\, and pet supplies—thoughtfully chosen and stocked with care 
 for pets of all kinds. We'll have other special vendors in attendance to s
 tay tuned - **Follow @wileyswish or @pawsarottispetshop on Instagram for u
 pdates!**\n\nWhether you’re ready to adopt\, love meeting dogs\, or just
  want an excuse to shop for your furry family member\, this is the perfect
  way to spend a spring Saturday.\n\n**🌼 Adopt 🦴 Shop 🐕 Fall in lo
 ve! See you March 21!**
LOCATION:Pawsarotti's Dog and Cat Boutique
URL:https://wileyswish.com/pages/news-events
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
