  music invites connection\, reflection\, and renewal. Join us for a soulfu
 l evening of song and community as we gather to mark the Spring Equinox to
 gether.**\n\nIG = @mamusemusic\n\nFB = https://www.facebook.com/MaMuseMu
 sic
