BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Hanging with Horses: Middle School
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T103000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T120000
UID:260305gckKjFFcEUCHVeA4_K_mDw
DESCRIPTION:A 4-week series of a screen-free space where middle schoolers 
 connect with horses\, feel supported\, and grow confidence.\n\nMiddle scho
 ol can be… a lot. Friendships changing. Siblings. Academic stress. Anxio
 us moments. Parents. You know. Horses are amazing friends\, guides\, liste
 ners\, and healers. They really know about relationships. AND they are exp
 erts at stress management. If you join Hanging with Horses\, you will hav
 e a blast and become a part of a wonderful herd \\(horses and humans.\\) Y
 ou might also...\n\nTry grounding and relaxation tools that actually help\
 n\nBuild confidence and leadership—just by being yourself\n\nLearn to sp
 eak horse while caring for the herd.\n\nYou don’t have to talk if you’
 re not ready. You don’t have to be “good with people.” You don’t n
 eed any horse experience.\n\nJust come as you are. The horses will meet yo
 u there 🐎✨\n\nThrough unpressured time “hanging with horses\,” gu
 ided group conversations\, and hands-on experiences\, participants will le
 arn to:\n\nUnderstand what stress and anxiety feel like in their own bodie
 s\n\nBuild healthier friendships and boundaries\n\nDevelop emotional aware
 ness and leadership skills\n\nPractice grounding and calming tools they ca
 n use anywhere\n\nGain confidence by tuning into themselves and their envi
 ronment\n\nHorses naturally reflect emotions and stress levels\, giving ki
 ds a powerful \\(and non-judgmental\\) way to learn about themselves and o
 thers.\n\n🐎NEIGH: Please come and check us out at an Open House for you
 th and parents: Speaking Horse ~ Year of the Fire Horse. \\(Free for Han
 ging with Horses families. Use the coupon code: MIDDLESCHOOL.\\) Register 
 here: https://www.eventbrite.com/e/1981488694024?aff=oddtdtcreator\n\nScho
 larships are available. Please reach out or schedule a call to request- He
 artMindEquine@gmail.com\n\nWHAT THE 4 WEEKS INCLUDE\n\nEach session blends
  horse time \\+ group connection\, with flexibility to meet the needs of t
 he group. \\(Purchase once for the 4 week series.\\)\n\nParticipants will:
 \n\nGet to know one another and create a safe\, respectful group space\n\n
 Explore friendship dynamics\, social pressure\, and anxiety \\(including s
 ocial media stress\\)\n\nKids are encouraged \\(but not pressured\\) to st
 ep slightly outside their comfort zones while always honoring their bounda
 ries.\n\nWHO THIS GROUP IS FOR\n\nThis group is ideal for middle schoolers
  who:\n\nFeel stressed\, anxious\, lonely\, or overwhelmed\n\nStruggle wit
 h friendships or social dynamics\n\nWant to build confidence and leadershi
 p skills\n\nFOR THE PARENTS\n\nMiddle school can be a stressful and emotio
 nally intense time. This 4-week equine-assisted services group offers a su
 pportive\, screen-free environment where kids can slow down\, build confid
 ence\, and learn healthy ways to manage stress and anxiety.
LOCATION:Heart & Mind Equine Horse Rescue
URL:https://www.eventbrite.com/e/hanging-with-horses-middle-school-tickets
 -1982833131272?aff=oddtdtcreator
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Therapeutic Group Hypnosis
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T140000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T160000
UID:260304yhYO78gGxk-VSEmKmCKflQ
DESCRIPTION:Guided into the calm presence of the Self\, you’ll understan
 d protective patterns\, meet vulnerable inner parts with curiosity instead
  of shame\, and gently release old emotional burdens.\n\nThrough inner dia
 logue and symbolic repair\, exiled parts are welcomed back as strengths—
 supporting deeper self-acceptance\, integration\, and emotional freedom. 
  You will be lead through this experience in a light hypnotic trance that
  is very relaxing and allows for accessing deeper layers of the subconscio
 us mind.\n\nEostar will close the group hypnotherapy session with a sound 
 bath\, enveloping everyone is a sonic embrace of heart-bliss.\n\nReturn at
  5 PM and join Eostar to further deepen into your heart-bliss during her S
 ound Odyssey.\n\nSOUND ODYSSEY\n\nAbout EESystem™\n\nThe EESystem™ is 
 a ecologically & environmentally safe system used by individuals\, doctors
 \, and therapists as well as Meditation and Wellness Centers to improve hu
 man development and psychological well-being.  Decades of documented res
 earch on the EESystem™ shows people experience improved immune function\
 , relief from pain\, detoxification\, elevated moods\, increased energy\, 
 and much more.\n\nAbout Eostar\n\nEostar Kamala is a multifaceted healer a
 nd musician\, specializing in therapeutic hypnosis\, transformational shad
 ow work\, and sound healing. With certifications from the Hypnosis Motivat
 ion Institute as a Master Hypnotist and Hypnotherapist\, she blends her ex
 tensive education—including breathwork facilitation and shamanic trainin
 g—with her passion for guiding others through their inner journeys.\n\nH
 er spiritual awakening began at 19 in Hungary\, ignited by the wisdom of a
  local healer. This transformative experience led her to explore various h
 ealing modalities\, ultimately culminating in the founding of “Shadow In
 to Light” Hypnotherapy. Eostar’s artistry reflects her journey\; from 
 sacred music performances to visual art representing her inner landscapes\
 , she channels universal love through every medium.\n\nNow based in Mount 
 Shasta’s energy vortex\, Eostar continues to evolve as a teacher and fac
 ilitator of plant medicine ceremonies while sharing her devotional music w
 ith the world. Her mission is to empower others to embrace their own paths
  toward healing and self-discovery.\n\nDiscover more about the Eostar’s 
 service to humanity at: Eostar.net/hypnotherapy/
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/eostar/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Sound Healing Odyssey
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T190000
UID:260304YIYw8K5TSk2W-kqJQgvprg
DESCRIPTION:Experience transpersonal states of consciousness\, pure bliss\
 , cessation of mind chatter\, accessing a full spectrum of emotions and re
 ceiving highly intuitive “downloads” as you immerse yourself in Eostar
 ’s Sound Healing Odyssey.\n\nRelease\, cleanse\, re-align body\, mind\, 
 soul and spirit\, using these ancient tools. Eostar’s sound journeys are
  meditations guided by the sound of various instruments\, with varying fre
 quencies and vibrations…most of which are rich in overtones that resonat
 e deeply in one’s body and auric field. These overtones can lead one int
 o a state of total relaxation in which healing and connection to a higher 
 consciousness usually happens spontaneously.\n\nEostar has played sacred a
 coustic music and sound healing music to audiences along the West Coast an
 d South America for more than two decades as a devotional musician and as 
 sound healer.  She creates sound-scapes using didgeridoo\, tank-drums\, k
 alimbas\, drums\, monochord\, crystal bowls\, chimes\, Tibetan bowls\, gui
 tar\, Gong and throat-singing.\n\nEostar is a Clinical Hypnotherapist and 
 breathwork teacher as well and she loves weaving these tools together with
  the sound bath experience she orchestrates.\n\nBegin your afternoon with 
 a journey to the heart during Eostar’s group hypnosis event in the EESys
 tem™  at 2 PM. \n\nGROUP HYPNOSIS\n\nAbout EESystem™​\n\nThe EESyst
 em™ is a ecologically & environmentally safe system used by individuals\
 , doctors\, and therapists as well as Meditation and Wellness Centers to i
 mprove human development and psychological well-being.  Decades of docum
 ented research on the EESystem™ shows people experience improved immune 
 function\, relief from pain\, detoxification\, elevated moods\, increased 
 energy\, and much more.\n\nAbout Eostar\n\nEostar Kamala is a multifaceted
  healer and musician\, specializing in therapeutic hypnosis\, transformati
 onal shadow work\, and sound healing. With certifications from the Hypnosi
 s Motivation Institute as a Master Hypnotist and Hypnotherapist\, she blen
 ds her extensive education—including breathwork facilitation and shamani
 c training—with her passion for guiding others through their inner journ
 eys.\n\nHer spiritual awakening began at 19 in Hungary\, ignited by the wi
 sdom of a local healer. This transformative experience led her to explore 
 various healing modalities\, ultimately culminating in the founding of "Sh
 adow Into Light" Hypnotherapy. Eostar’s artistry reflects her journey\; 
 from sacred music performances to visual art representing her inner landsc
 apes\, she channels universal love through every medium.\n\nNow based in M
 ount Shasta’s energy vortex\, Eostar continues to evolve as a teacher an
 d facilitator of plant medicine ceremonies while sharing her devotional mu
 sic with the world. Her mission is to empower others to embrace their own 
 paths toward healing and self-discovery.\n\nDiscover more about Eostar's m
 ulti-disciplinary acoustic talents at: Eostar.net/sound-healing/
LOCATION:Energy Wave Center
URL:https://energywavecenter.com/sound-odyssey/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
