DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T233000
UID:260130hhi1smkct0GzGTWYpbHe5w
DESCRIPTION:Weekly Sunday Karaoke at Barrel Proof Lounge! Hosted by AJ the
  KJ. Starts at 8PM — bring your voice & your friends! Presented by Razor
  Entertainment | Hosted by AJ the KJ\n\nYour new Sunday night ritual is he
 re — Karaoke Night at Barrel Proof Lounge \, right in the heart of downt
 own Santa Rosa.\n\nHosted by the one and only AJ the KJ \, and powered by 
 Razor Entertainment \, this weekly sing-along throwdown brings the perfect
