UID:260113WvGWSmfhdUS_BFJOZGh6cA
DESCRIPTION:Weekend Workshop: March 21 & 22\n\nSpend a weekend exploring t
 he traditional art of paper mache. In this two-day workshop\, you’ll beg
 in by building inner structures from recycled materials\, creating sturdy 
 frames for your sculptures before layering paper mache made from flour and
  water.\n\nBertha will share folk-art traditions from Mexico\, guiding you
  through sculpting\, layering\, and painting your finished piece.
