BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Clover Sonoma Family Fun Series: The Pout-Pout Fish by TheaterWork
 sUSA
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T153000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260322T153000
UID:260311os_V003Q0kSIyG_vI-2v5g
DESCRIPTION:Back to All Shows\n\nClover Sonoma Family Fun Series\n\nThe Po
 ut-Pout Fish \n\nby TheaterWorksUSA\n\nSunday\, March 22\, 2026\n\n3:30 pm
 \n\nBUY TICKETS \n\nIndividual Tickets go on sale for Members beginning Au
 gust 19\; General Public\, August 22 \n\n \n\nCan the poutiest fish frown 
 turn upside down? Find out in this extraordinary musical\, featuring whims
 ical puppets and live performers in a sweeping oceanic adventure. When Mr.
  Fish sets out on a quest to find Miss Clam’s missing pearl\, he discove
 rs there is more to him than his permanently plastered pout. Dive into thi
 s colorful adaptation of The New York Times bestseller\, co-conceived\, 
 directed\, and designed by the acclaimed puppeteers of AchesonWalsh Studio
 s\, whose work was featured in Broadway’s The King And I\, On the Town
  and Radio City’s New York Spectacular. The writing team includes New V
 ictory LabWorks Residency recipients Christopher Anselmo\, Jared Corak\, M
 att Acheson\, and Fergus Walsh. \n\nRecommended for ages 3-8\, however\, y
 ou know your child best. \n\nRun Time: 50 minutes \n\nLap passes available
  day of the show\, in-person at the ticket office for ages 2 and under. \n
 \nLBC performance may not include pieces from above video. \n\n \n\nFamily
  Fun in the Lobby\n\nStarting one hour before each performance\, please jo
 in us in the lobby for fun art projects uniquely developed for each show. 
 It’s a fun\, free way for adults and children alike to get creative\, wh
 ile enhancing your enjoyment of the show. We also have pizza\, beverages\,
  and snacks available\, all priced with a family’s budget in mind!   \n
 \nVIPs Meet the Cast\n\nSubscription holders be sure to stick around after
  the show to meet the cast and get autographs! \\(Except The Peking Acroba
 ts®.\\) \n\n Family Fun Series – Save 20% and see all 5 shows!\n\nSee t
 he full series here: Clover Sonoma Family Fun Series \n\nTimeline\n\nNew S
 ubscriptions go on sale for Members beginning June 24\; General Public\, J
 une 27.\n\nIndividual Tickets go on sale for Members beginning August 19\;
  General Public\, August 22.\n\nTwo ways to buy! Season ticket packages ar
 e available online or by downloading the form \\(linked below\\) and sendi
 ng the completed form to us by mail or email. If you have any questions\, 
 call the Patron & Member Services Office at 707.546.3600. \n\nPurchase New
  Subscription ONLINE\n\nDownload New Subscription Form \n\nTHIRD PARTY RES
 ELLERS\n\nDon’t get taken by deceptive online resellers who use bots to 
 buy tickets and then mark up their prices. The only safe way to protect yo
 ur purchase and guarantee the best seats at the lowest cost is to work dir
 ectly with us: through our website\, by phone\, or at our box office in Sa
 nta Rosa. Plus\, we’re not bots. Our friendly team members are easily ac
 cessible by phone or at the box office to provide customer support.
LOCATION:Luther Burbank Center for the Arts
URL:https://lutherburbankcenter.org/event/fam-pout-pout-fish25/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
