DESCRIPTION:Tiny Hooves\, Big Hearts: Our Ongoing Rescue Mission\n\nAt Goa
 tlandia\, our mission is simple: to give love\, safety\, and a second chan
 ce to animals who need it most.\n\nWe were recently called to rescue three
  baby goats. These tiny babies are now safe at Goatlandia\, and they need 
 bottle feeding several times a day to stay healthy and thrive.\n\nThat’s
  Where You Come In: The Bottle Baby Breakfast Club\n\nStarting March 6th\,
  join us for a heartwarming hour on the farm\, bottle-feeding and cuddling
  our newest rescues while supporting their care.\n\nYour $250 donation \\(
 covers milk and supplies for weeks of feedings\\) includes admission for u
 p to four guests for a private\, unforgettable visit to Goatlandia.\n\nCom
 e share the love\, feel the magic\, and help us give these little ones the
