UID:260311bM5jTP4llEWjWcEJHeX7Lw
DESCRIPTION:Everyone needs access to health care\, yet health care is beco
 ming increasingly unaffordable. Can California lead the way for the rest o
 f our country and enact single-payer?\n\nFind out more on Monday\, March 2
 3 at 6:30 PM at the Sonoma Valley Democrats Virtual General Meeting when T
 erry Winter\, RN\, presents "Now is the Time for Single-Payer in CA." Terr
 y has worked in Sonoma County as a registered nurse and specialist in heal
 th policy for 40 years. He is now on the leadership team of the Healthcare
  for All Working Group.\n\nEveryone is welcome to attend at no charge and 
 there will be time for Q & A. To receive the Zoom link\, email: contact@
 svdems.org
URL:https://www.svdems.org/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
