DESCRIPTION:Discover your family story at our Family Search Center You wil
 l find our center in the Lakeport building in the room next to the nursery
 . Local volunteers can help jumpstart your family history journey. Our cen
 ter is staffed on Tuesdays from 1pm - 4pm\, reach us in person or by phone
  \\(707\\) 280-9545 during those hours. All services provided in centers a
 re free. You’ll enjoy: Personalized help Center guests can receive perso
 nal help from volunteers in one of more than 5\,400 centers worldwide. Acc
 ess to technology Centers offer complimentary access to computers\, intern
 et\, and subscription family history websites. Available resources vary by
  location. Access to exclusive records Visitors to FamilySearch Centers ge
 t special access to images of historical records that are only available i
 n centers. Websites available at all locations: Ancestry\, My Heritage\, F
 amily Search\, Find My Past\, American Ancestors\, Geneanet https://www.fa
 mily search.org Explore videos about family history and temples at collect
 ion/temple-and-family-history-messages-from-leaders?lang=eng
