BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Stitch Together 🧵
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T190000
UID:260124JWJGUvAzC02ySLKT5xP9Ug
DESCRIPTION:Join us for **Stitch Café**\, a cozy open studio held twice a
  month. Whether you're working on your own project or eager to explore new
  mending techniques like darning and appliqué\, this is the perfect space
  to gather\, share ideas\, and sew together. We provide hand-sewing suppli
 es and materials\, but feel free to bring your own - it's all about commun
 ity\, creativity\, and enjoying the process.By repairing what we already h
 ave and re-using materials\, we're not just preserving memories and adding
  unique touches to our belongings - we’re also reducing waste and contri
 buting to a more sustainable lifestyle. We can extend the life of our clot
 hes and fabrics\, and take small but meaningful steps toward caring for th
 e planet.
LOCATION:Art Escape
URL:https://artescapesonoma.jumbula.com/Spring2026/StitchTogether325
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
