DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260325T160000
UID:2509171TEJjSOY-ki-D8TCbhR6Aw
DESCRIPTION:Explore the heart and soul of winemaking with our Grape to Gla
 ss Tour & Tasting at Dutton Estate Winery. Immerse yourself in the world o
 f wine as you stroll through our chardonnay vineyard\, rooted in six gener
 ations of farming legacy in the heart of the Russian River Valley. Witness
  firsthand the art and passion behind our winemaking process with an exclu
 sive tour of our modest crush pad and barrel room. Relish with a tasting o
 f five current releases and a special library wine\, accompanied with a cu
 rated cheese and charcuterie board\, and finished with decadent artisanal 
 chocolates. Note: This tasting experience requires a 48-hour advanced rese
 rvation.\n\n$95 per guest | Special Club Member Pricing
LOCATION:Dutton Estate Winery
URL:https://www.duttonestate.com/visit-us/tasting-reservations/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
