DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T190000
UID:260211K31chaLmP06P8kAQRLnb8w
DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Women With Vision for Women's History Month\n\nWome
 n’s stories want to be told. It's Women's History Month. Let’s lift 
 the voices of women with vision from cultures across the world and celebra
 te them through story and poetry with readings from local authors Anna Cit
 rino\, Jean Gordon Kocienda\, and Pamela Reitman. \n\nStories hold the w
 orld together and help us see ourselves in others' lives. Come share a me
 al and listen to a few stories of some amazing women.\n\nTo RSVP \\(Requir
 ed\\) see: https://aqus.com/communitydinnerRSVP/\n\nTo learn more about A
 qus Cafe Community Dinners\, see: https://aqus.com/communitydinners/
