BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Jane Siberry
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T200000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260326T200000
UID:251021XsgztuJAekydIltW8aeF5A
DESCRIPTION:Jane Siberry\, a highly respected artist in the international 
 music scene for over four decades\, is embarking on a North American tour 
 from November 5 to December 3\, 2024. Known for her ethereal voice and gen
 re-defying sound\, she has released 15 studio albums and is debuting new m
 usic inspired by the pandemic\, released one song at a time. Her live perf
 ormances are celebrated for their emotional depth\, storytelling\, and spo
 ntaneous magic\, blending classics with new reflections on resilience and 
 human endurance. This tour exemplifies Jane's creative evolution and endur
 ing commitment to meaningful artistry.
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/1036645040?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=2
 87&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Longboard Vineyards Wine\, Dine & Dance
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T170000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T190000
UID:251224xrDLQVFbtEm2qN2kb47gSw
DESCRIPTION:Friday Night Music\, Wine & Dine at Longboard Vineyards\n\nFea
 turing Rock on a Roll & Lila’s Streetside Eats\n\nJoin us for a high-ene
 rgy Friday night at Longboard Vineyards in our Barrel Room\, located in do
 wntown Healdsburg\, featuring live music\, award-winning wine\, and bold s
 treet-style food. Our Music\, Wine & Dine Night pairs the fun\, crowd-plea
 sing sounds of Rock on a Roll with the flavorful dishes of Lila’s Street
 side Eats.\n\nRock on a Roll brings an upbeat mix of familiar favorites an
 d danceable tunes\, creating the perfect soundtrack for a relaxed and soci
 al evening surrounded by barrels and warm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longboard
 ’s wines by the glass or bottle while Lila’s Streetside Eats serves fr
 esh\, creative street food made to order and packed with flavor.\n\nFriday
  | 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 event
  inside the Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome on t
 he patio only.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma County
  night of great music\, great wine\, and great food.\n\nWine available for
  purchase Live music by Rock on a Roll Food by Lila’s Streetside Eats \\
 (street-style comfort food\\) Location: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Ad
 dress: 5 Fitch Street\, Healdsburg\, CA 95448
LOCATION:Longboard Vineyards
URL:https://www.longboardvineyards.com
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
