 al evening surrounded by barrels and warm winery ambiance. Enjoy Longboard
 ’s wines by the glass or bottle while Lila’s Streetside Eats serves fr
 esh\, creative street food made to order and packed with flavor.\n\nFriday
  | 5:00 PM – 7:00 PM Free entry\n\nPlease note: This is an over-21 event
  inside the Barrel Room. Under-21 guests and leashed pets are welcome on t
 he patio only.\n\nCome grab a seat early and enjoy a classic Sonoma County
  night of great music\, great wine\, and great food.\n\nWine available for
  purchase Live music by Rock on a Roll Food by Lila’s Streetside Eats \\
 (street-style comfort food\\) Location: Longboard Vineyards Barrel Room Ad
