BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Lúnasa
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T200000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260327T200000
UID:260114824gR7w_WU2hIRtXWpuiLg
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a magical evening of Irish music as world-renowned
  Celtic ensemble Lúnasa takes the stage at the Sebastopol Community Cultu
 ral Center.\n\nHailed as “the hottest Irish acoustic band on the planet
 ” \\(The New York Times\\)\, Lúnasa has thrilled audiences around the g
 lobe with their innovative arrangements and exceptional musicianship. Blen
 ding traditional melodies with contemporary flair\, the group has redefine
 d Irish music for a new generation—while honoring its deep roots.\n\nWit
 h a lineup featuring flute\, fiddle\, pipes\, and guitar\, Lúnasa’s dyn
 amic performances are rich with rhythm\, texture\, and soul. Whether you'r
 e a longtime fan or discovering them for the first time\, this is an unfor
 gettable live experience you won’t want to miss.
LOCATION:Sebastopol Community Cultural Center
URL:https://www.bandsintown.com/e/107422461?app_id=pkvts0on0m&came_from=28
 7&utm_medium=api&utm_source=partner_api&utm_campaign=event
