 ue. Then\, follow the clues as you visit participating storefronts and exp
 lore the courtyard. Once you’ve completed the hunt\, return to Copperfie
 ld’s Books to collect your goodie bag prize.\n\nIt’s the perfect way t
 o spend the morning\, learning\, exploring\, and making memories together 
 at Montgomery Village.
LOCATION:Montgomery Village Courtyard
URL:https://montgomeryvillageca.com/event/lesson-for-littles/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
