DESCRIPTION:Join the City of Cotati for the second annual Climate Ready Co
 tati Fair on March 28\, 2026 from 10-2 at the Cotati SMART Depot (970 E Co
 tati Avenue\, Cotati\, CA 94931). The Fair is FREE and will feature 40 l
 ocal agencies and organizations sharing resources\, information\, and idea
 s to help you live a more sustainable lifestyle and have a positive impact
  on the environment. Cotati's own Sal's Pizza and Dogs A La Carte will off
 er great food for sale\, featuring reusable dishes provided by Sparkl Reus
 ables to reduce disposables waste. Prize giveaways\, kids’ activities\, 
 an e-waste dropoff\, small appliance repair\, and much more will be availa
 ble at this awesome event. Join us for activities to help you reduce\, reu
 se\, and recycle... and have fun!\n\nVisit the Climate Ready Cotati Fair w
 ebpage for more information: https://bit.ly/CRCFair2026
