DESCRIPTION:Join us for on the farm on **Saturday\, March 28\, 2026**\, f
 or a Day of Service honoring farm worker rights activists César Chávez a
 nd Dolores Huerta.\n\nWe’ll have volunteer activities from 9 a.m. to noo
 n.\n\nSign up for a spot at Calendly.com/PetalumaBounty\n\nKids are welco
 me with an accompanying adult.\n\nAs César Chávez Day\, March 31\, appro
 aches\, we reflect on the legacy of Chávez and Huerta\, who bravely foug
 ht the injustices and exploitative labor practices of California’s bigge
 st agribusinesses. We reflect on all farmworkers’ ongoing and often unsu
 ng contributions to society.
