DESCRIPTION:Traverse century-old logging roads through lush riparian zones
 \, open rangelands with coastal views\, and serene silvopasture. The 1.5-m
 ile trail includes a 400-foot elevation gain — and a scenic descent back
  down.\n\nBring sturdy shoes and water for this rewarding trek through The
  Sea Ranch’s diverse landscapes! Note: Steep sections may be challenging
  for those with mobility limitations. Due to safety considerations\, dogs 
 are not permitted.\n\n\\*Max 25 guests\, ages 7+
LOCATION:The Sea Ranch Lodge 
URL:https://www.thesearanchlodge.com/programming/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
