UID:2602280XBIfX9S_UuYJOZHBbrIMQ
DESCRIPTION:Homeward Bound 12x12 acrylic\n\nMary McDougall is a retired po
 tter turned painter. As a painter her first love is landscapes\, as she sa
 ys\, “It is all about Mother Earth”. Living in the midst of such beaut
 y\, her paintings often depict the quiet serenity and explosive color of t
 he trees\, rolling hills\, vineyards\, wildflowers and coastal views. Mary
  is a member of Sky Ranch Gallery in Tomales and is the Featured Artist fo
 r the month of March with her acrylics and watercolors.
