DESCRIPTION:Join us for an immersive sound healing experience guided by De
 borah Johnsen\, longtime yoga teacher\, sound healer\, and wellness guide 
 for The Sea Ranch community. Since 2000\, Deborah has led yoga classes and
  explored many paths of wellness. She weaves together yogic wisdom\, medit
 ation\, and the vibrations of crystal and Tibetan bowls to create a restor
 ative journey for body\, mind\, and spirit.\n\nThrough the soothing resona
 nce of these sacred instruments\, you will be invited into a state of deep
  relaxation\, balance\, and renewal. Each session is more than a personal 
 practice. It is an opportunity to rest\, receive\, and connect more deeply
  with yourself and the community around you.\n\nRegistration required. To 
 register\, email megan@thesearanchlodge.com. Please plan to arrive at 3:45
 .
LOCATION:The Sea Ranch Lodge 
URL:https://www.thesearanchlodge.com/programming/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
