BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Heart-opening Cacao Ceremony & Yoga
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260329T123000
UID:260312SJEL-KXf10aosTyi39A80w
DESCRIPTION:Join us at The Sea Ranch Lodge for an unforgettable experience
 . Tap into new levels of joy as you open your heart and tune into your sen
 ses during an ancestral Cacao Ceremony led by Charlotte Keane and Heart Op
 ening yoga session led by Shoshana Hebshi.\n\nThe ceremonial cacao drink w
 ill be prepared and consumed in the ritual shared by Charlotte’s ancesto
 rs. As a plant medicine\, cacao itself calls us to share her loving energy
  with others. Paired with drums\, rattles\, and movement you will be able 
 to tap into new levels of joy and exhilaration. Priestess Charlotte brings
  ritual and ceremonial customs from her family in Mexico\, Central and Sou
 th America. She is a healer\, shaman\, curandera\, and ordained priestess 
 in the Order of the Magdalene. Shoshana is the founder and owner of Revolu
 tion Yoga in Santa Rosa. She has been practicing yoga for more than 20 yea
 rs\, and as an instructor aims to nurture the same spirit of joy\, connect
 ion and calmness that was lit for her by her teachers.
LOCATION:The Sea Ranch Lodge 
URL:https://www.thesearanchlodge.com/programming/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Brandlin Estate Wine & Food Tasting Experience
