UID:251213tcknK8YQ7kixSTmIVIYogA
DESCRIPTION:This class is designed for dancers who have a solid grasp of t
 he basics and are eager to expand their repertoire with more complex and f
 luid movements.\n\nPre- requisite:\n\nSalsa Class Beginners\n\nEach week\,
  we’ll break down a new move\, focusing on the technique and connection 
 that will make you a more confident and stylish dancer. We’ll go beyond 
 the foundational steps to cover a wide range of essential intermediate pat
 terns and styling\, including:\n\nTurns and Spins:\n\nMaster your inside a
 nd outside turns\, double spins\, and the elegant 360 and Hand Toss moves.
 \n\nIntricate Patterns:\n\nLearn to execute the 360\, wrap\, as well as va
 rious Cross Body Lead variations like the U-Turn and Spiral.\n\nFootwork a
 nd Styling:\n\nEnhance your rhythm and flair with advanced footwork like t
 he Suzy Q\, Front Tap\, and Mambo Step. We’ll also work on styling with 
 a wrap and improving your posture and upper body movement.\n\nThis class i
 s your chance to refine your technique\, improve your lead-follow connecti
 on\, and add a variety of fun and dynamic moves to your salsa vocabulary. 
 Join us and elevate your dance!\n\nDetails:\n\nNo partner necessary — ro
 tations ensure everyone gets to dance.\n\nPlease wear non-marking shoe so
 les to protect the floor.\n\nArrive 10 minutes early to warm up and get s
 ettled.\n\nDate & Time: Tuesdays @ 6:30PM – 7:30PM
LOCATION:Salsa Dance Marin
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/intermediate-salsa-clas
 s/17159571/2026-03-31T18
