DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T000000
UID:260224bj6zga-7Okys1PD0LDV4WA
DESCRIPTION:Cedar Roots’ electro-folk set is a weaving of silk and honey
  harmonies over raw acoustic guitar\, carried by earthy\, grounding beats.
 \n\nThis is music rooted in the land but reaching toward the sky\, echoes 
 of campfire songs filtered through analog warmth and modern rhythm. Expect
  heart-opening vocals\, foot-stomping grooves\, and stories that feel like
  old friends. A sound that is both tender and electric\, grounded and tran
 scendent.
LOCATION:Soft Medicine Sanctuary
