DESCRIPTION:Downtown Santa Rosa 'Golden Hour' 4-7p| Live music 5-7 p | $6 
 beers & $2 off wine |Tuesday-Saturday!\n\nFor people who like to party...b
 ut want to be home at a reasonable hour...Welcome to **Live Music - The Uk
 ulele Ramblers - Open Uke Jam!** Join us for a fun-filled evening of live 
 music and ukulele jamming at Barrel Proof Lounge. Bring your ukulele and s
 trum along with The Ukulele Ramblers\, a talented group of musicians who w
 ill be performing a mix of classic tunes and original songs. Whether you'r
 e a seasoned ukulele player or a beginner looking to learn\, this event is
  perfect for all music lovers. So mark your calendars and get ready to enj
 oy a night of great music and good vibes. See you there!\n\nOpen Uke jam h
 osted by your friendly neighborhood Ukulele collective.\n\nBring your sing
 ing voice and your Uke if you've got one\, and enjoy the comfortable\, wel
 coming space at Barrel Proof Lounge! 21+ Happy Hour Pricing 4-6pm All beer
 s - $6 + $2 off wine. Live Music 5-7pm 2 drink minimum\, please\n\n**www.U
 kuleleRamblers.net** Check out **www.BarrelProofLounge.com** for all sor
 ts of good times ahead!
