BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Mobility Class with Efren
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T100000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260401T100000
UID:251216k6_v9gm8oUCO5tsKJ1U70w
DESCRIPTION:This Movement-Fusion class is designed to build foundational m
 obility\, deep flexibility\, and graceful flow. It is a unique practice fo
 cused on systematically opening the body\, enhancing your ability to move 
 with ease\, and creating more internal space.\n\nYou will leave feeling st
 ronger\, lighter\, and more profoundly connected to your body’s potentia
 l. This class is perfect for athletes\, dancers\, and anyone looking to si
 gnificantly improve their overall quality of movement and physical comfort
 .\n\nAbout Efren\n\nA health-fitness educator and mentor with over 15 year
 s of experience leading group exercise classes\, including aerobics\, stre
 tching\, strength training\, Zumba\, and dance workouts. AFAA\, NASM\, an
 d trained as a Myofascial Release and Precision NMT—TMJ Myofascial Pra
 ctitioner.\n\nToday\, I integrate a holistic approach to movement\, blend
 ing the principles of mind-body connection.\n\nWhat to bring: yoga mat\, t
 owel and yoga block as well or anything you need to support your practice.
  We usually do class barefoot. \n\nDate & Time: EVERY FIRST SUNDAY IN TH
 E MONTH 10 am \\(see our schedule for availability\\)\n\nAddress: 4140 Red
 wood Highway \\#8 San Rafael\, CA\n\nNote: Arrive 10 minutes before. No fl
 oor marking shoe soles allowed.
LOCATION:4140 Redwood Highway #8
URL:https://salsadancemarin.com/mobility-2/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
