 bit of magic!  WWW.ARTNITEHEALDSBURG.COM Find the gallery map and a list o
 f participating restaurants and wineries online. Pick up your ARTNITE pass
 port available at any downtown gallery\, and start your journey anywhere! 
 \\#artnitehealdsburg From 5pm - 7pm every 1st Thursday of the month Thank 
 you to @stayhealsburg and @healdsburgchamber for sponsoring our event thro
