 t Copy fees are applicable for all when researching in-house Carpooling is
  recommended due to limited parking. Members & guests can meet at the Vall
 ejo Naval & Historical Museum \\(734 Marin Street in Vallejo\\) back parki
 ng lot at 9:45 am to carpool. The library tour begins at 10:30 am.
