 elcome to attend. Snacks will be provided. Common Ground Society serves fa
 milies who have loved ones with any sort of unique need while also educati
 ng our community on how to be inclusive. Held the 1st Friday of the month 
 from 10:30-11:30am. We will not be meeting in January. 12/05/2025- Decembe
 r's title is Unfit Parent : A Disabled Mother Challenges An Inaccessible W
 orld by Jessica Slice 2/06/2025- Disability Intimacy: Essays on Love\, Car
 e\, and Desire: Edited by Alice Wong 3/06/2025- The Kiss Quotient by Helen
  Hoang 04/03/2025- True Biz by Sara Nović 05/01/2025- Second Life: Having
