UID:2602124duoXCrfskuQ5Pri4Dk8zg
DESCRIPTION:We’re excited to announce that the OAEC Nursery is reopening
  on April 3rd! The OAEC Nursery is a nonprofit nursery dedicated to uplift
 ing ecologically and culturally important plants\, focusing on perennial f
 ood\, medicinal\, and native varieties\, and an ever-evolving selection of
  annual food crops. The event will take place April 3rd and 4th\, from 11 
 am - 5 pm\, and will feature live music and a public tour on Saturday the 
 4th at 1 pm. For our reopening in 2026\, we are making a couple of big cha
 nges: we are expanding our hours to Wednesday through Saturday from 11 am 
 - 5 pm\, and we’ll be staying open year-round!
