UID:260312umpRYTj7C0m78JgkkoXfqw
DESCRIPTION:Join author **Monte Schulz** as he talks about\, reads from\
 , and signs his newest novel\, *Undercity*. Schulz has written several bo
 oks\, including *Crossing Eden* and *Naughty*\, and released the innovati
 ve album *Seraphonium*. His latest book is a companion to his award-winni
 ng novel ***Metropolis***\, and dives deeper into the upside-down dystopi
 an underground labyrinth of cast-outs\, misanthropes\, and disenfranchise
 d masses. Monte Schulz is the son of *Peanuts* creator and cartoonist Ch
 arles M. Schulz.
LOCATION:Charles M. Schulz Museum
URL:https://schulzmuseum.org/monte-schulz-undercity/
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
