DESCRIPTION:WHAT: Markham Vineyards Private Tasting: The Cabernet Connoiss
 eur’s Experience\n\nDATE:            Begins October 1\, 2025\,
  Offered Daily\n\nTIME: 11am-1pm and 2-4pm\n\nWHERE:       Markham Vi
 neyards\n\n                        2812 St Helena H
 wy North\, St Helena\, CA 94574\n\n                   
      707-963-5292\n\n                        ht
 tps://markhamvineyards.com/ \n\nLINK:             https://mark
 hamvineyards.com/visit/winery-experiences/\n\nDETAILS:\n\nDiscover the pin
 nacle of Markham Cabernet Sauvignon. This privately guided tasting feature
 s rare library vintages\, limited single-vineyard wines\, and an exclusive
  barrel tasting of The Philanthropist\, our flagship 100% Cabernet Sauvign
 on\, expertly paired with local cheeses\, charcuterie\, and chocolates. A 
 collector’s journey through the past\, present\, and future of Napa Vall
 ey Cabernet.\n\nEach booking is private and guided by a dedicated Ambassad
 or. Guests will also step inside the Markham winery to sample a yet-to-be-
 released vintage of The Philanthropist Cabernet Sauvignon from a French Oa
 k barrel.\n\n·         Offered Daily: 11:00 am – 1:00 pm and 2:
 00 – 4:00 pm\n\n·         Experience length: 2 hours\n\n·  
        Wines: Selections of library\, limited single-vineyard\, and 
 a barrel tasting of yet-to-be-released Cabernet Sauvignon\n\n·     
     Cost: $150 per Person\n\n·         Exclusive Member Price:
  $95 per Member\n\nADMISSION: Members $95 | Non-members $150
LOCATION:Markham Vineyards
URL:https://www.pressdemocrat.com/events/#/details/markham-vineyards-priva
 te-tasting-the-cabernet-connoisseur-s-experience/16955378/2026-04-05T11
