 ker or just starting to learn\, this is a perfect way to practice Spanish 
 in a relaxed\, wine-filled setting.   Cost: $15 (+ tax) per person •  
   Includes one glass of wine or zero-proof verjus spritz •    2 round
 s of Loteria •    Chances to win prizes\n\nAdditional wine purchases a
 vailable Empanadas available for $15 (+ tax)   No Spanish experience nece
 ssary - come ready to learn\, laugh\, and enjoy some delicious wine!\n\nWa
 lk-ins welcome based on availability. Please allow up to 30 minutes for em
 panadas\, preorders recommended.
LOCATION:Keller Estate 
URL:https://kellerestate.com/blogs/event/loteria
X-SOURCE:Press Democrat
END:VEVENT
