BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Nurturing our Heart with the Guided Wisdom of Horses - Two Session
  Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T090000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260408T130000
UID:260306HzBMJvUwJkip_hRF6RwPVQ
DESCRIPTION:Through  Hands-On experiences\, you’ll be guided to access y
 our own inner wisdom supported by the intuitive and healing energy of the 
 horses.
LOCATION:Forget Me Not Farm
